# mbsync config — copy to ~/.mbsyncrc and edit USER lines.
#
# kb-capture: dedicated capture inbox for cl ingest (sub-project 03).
# Add additional IMAPAccount blocks below for your main Gmail or other accounts.

IMAPAccount kb-capture
Host imap.gmail.com
User <YOUR-CAPTURE-ADDRESS>@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.config/mbsync/kb-capture-password"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore kb-capture-remote
Account kb-capture

MaildirStore kb-capture-local
Path ~/mail/kb-capture/
Inbox ~/mail/kb-capture/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel kb-capture
Far :kb-capture-remote:
Near :kb-capture-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
SyncState *
Expunge None
